1. [Hiroyuki Shinoda, Hiromasa Chigusa, and Yasutoshi Makino: Flexible Tactile Sensor Skin Using Wireless Sensor Elements Coupled with 2D Microwaves, Journal of Robotics and Mechatronics, Vol.22 No.6, pp.784-789, Dec. 2010.](http://www.fujipress.jp/finder/xslt.php?mode=present&inputfile=ROBOT002200060013.xml)
1. [Hiroyuki Shinoda, Yasutoshi Makino, Naoshi Yamahira, and Hiroto Itai: Surface Sensor Network Using Inductive Signal Transmission Layer, Proc. 4th International Conference on Networked Sensing Systems (INSS 2007), pp. 201-206, 2007.](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WXjk5jKbZBtRQxDunTtcA6GxRaJe9ZYx/view?usp=sharing)
1. [篠田裕之： 素材表面に形成する高速センサネットワーク，計測と制御，Vol. 46, No. 2, pp.98-103, 2007.](https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/sicejl1962/46/2/46_2_98/_pdf)
